ygData.messageBody:
NOOOOOOO... I missed another wedding! =( I had company in town all last week and
didn't check my eMail once (missed out on alot of other things too). I'm so
sorry. How was it? Did it go over well? What little details do you wish you'd
planned ahead of time? What advice would you give someone planning a wedding in
the near future? *clears her throat and grins shyly*

And how many people would be interested in attending a wedding on Povar? And what
are some sites you all would recommend for a wedding for two 20th level
characters? Please, anyone feel free to answer. I have absolutely no ideas at
the present (course I still have a couple levels to go, and we level slowly, so
it could be late December before we actually hit 20) and would welcome ANY.

Sara/Aelwesara, Povar
